            <Ritual>
                        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
                                    <ab>VrS31.18 (ms. 2000):</ab>
                                    <ab class="ab_indent">
                                                zōt ud rāspīg <em>yə̄ səuuištō ahurō mazdā̊scā ... mōi ādāi kahiiāicīt̰ paitī</em> sē bār guftan ud pad harw bār-ē hōm pad <em>kahiiāicīt̰ paitī</em> afšārdan</ab>  
                                    <ab class="ab_indent">
                                                "The <em>zōt</em> and the <em>rāspīg</em> should recite three times <em>yə̄ səuuištō ahurō mazdā̊scā ... mōi ādāi kahiiāicīt̰ paitī</em>. Each time,
                                                he should strain the <em>hōm</em> at <em>kahiiāicīt̰ paitī</em>."</ab>
                        </Nerangs>
            </Ritual>
